            <p class="cookie-page-lead">
                This notice explains how the main HelloUniversity platform may use session cookies, local storage, analytics, and similar technologies to keep the site working, support account access, remember preferences, and understand service performance.
            </p>

            <div class="cookie-page-meta">
                <span class="cookie-page-chip">Last updated: March 16, 2026</span>
