        <div class="cookie-page-card-grid">
            <article class="app-panel cookie-page-card">
                <span class="material-icons cookie-page-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">verified_user</span>
                <h3>Essential session and security cookies</h3>
                <p>These help keep users signed in, maintain authenticated sessions, apply security settings, and support reliable platform access.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="app-panel cookie-page-card">
                <span class="material-icons cookie-page-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">tune</span>
                <h3>Preference storage</h3>
                <p>Some pages may store interface choices such as theme or similar user preferences so the site can remember them between visits.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="app-panel cookie-page-card">
                <span class="material-icons cookie-page-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">monitoring</span>
