            </article>

            <article class="app-panel cookie-page-card">
                <span class="material-icons cookie-page-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">extension</span>
                <h3>Third-party service cookies</h3>
                <p>Some public pages may load third-party services such as site search or advertising scripts, and those providers may use their own cookies or similar technologies.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
